OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 04 JUN
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1984FThe first episode of US series
OL,7,FManimal airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1993FTonight's edition of Have I Got
OL,10,FNews for You - which went out at 10pm
OL,11,Fon BBC Two - saw Roy Hattersley
OL,12,Freplaced by a tub of lard. Mr
OL,13,FHattersley failed to turn up for the
OL,14,Fprogramme recording. This was
OL,15,Fapparently the third time he had
OL,16,Fcancelled at the last minute. The tub
OL,17,Fof lard was credited at the end of the
OL,18,Fprogramme: "The Rt. Hon. Tub of Lard
OL,19,FMP".
